We have $\sqrt{2}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} = \sqrt{2}\left(1+\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\right) = \sqrt{2}(1+\sqrt{2})$.  Similarly, $\sqrt{3}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}} = \sqrt{3}(1+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}})$.

Adding these two expressions together, we get: $$\sqrt{2}(1+\sqrt{2}) + \sqrt{3}(1+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}) = \sqrt{2}+2\sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+1+\frac{\sqrt{3}}{\sqrt{3}}$$

This simplifies to: $$\sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 = \sqrt{2}+\sqrt{3}+3 